00:19:05.560 --> 00:19:10.560
In terms of challenges of those multilingual workflows

00:19:10.719 --> 00:19:14.239
for notebooks, I think it's worth mentioning

00:19:14.239 --> 00:19:17.760
that when you add those polyglot capabilities,

00:19:18.839 --> 00:19:21.760
there are certain complexities that emerge.

00:19:21.760 --> 00:19:25.560
One of them is that debugging across different languages

00:19:25.560 --> 00:19:27.520
can become very challenging

00:19:27.520 --> 00:19:31.520
because you can be the new Python, R, SQL,

00:19:31.520 --> 00:19:33.680
Julia and so on.

00:19:33.719 --> 00:19:38.719
Managing dependencies can also have additional challenges

00:19:39.079 --> 00:19:40.520
because you have multiple languages,

00:19:40.520 --> 00:19:42.920
multiple dependencies and so on.

00:19:42.920 --> 00:19:46.119
And often you are also running,

00:19:47.319 --> 00:19:50.680
let's say Python, if you want to run Python in R,

00:19:50.680 --> 00:19:53.359
for example, it might be using reticulate

00:19:53.359 --> 00:19:58.319
or the other way around with the R2Pi extension and so on.

00:19:58.319 --> 00:20:00.719
So those dependencies can also be challenging.

00:20:01.719 --> 00:20:06.079
Third, we can have some performance overhead

00:20:06.079 --> 00:20:09.880
as a result of that language creation.

00:20:09.880 --> 00:20:13.319
And then we have the challenge of the team knowledge,

00:20:13.319 --> 00:20:15.719
knowledge requirement can increase

00:20:15.719 --> 00:20:18.760
because suddenly the person who's in Python

00:20:18.760 --> 00:20:21.520
needs to know some R, SQL and so on.

00:20:22.359 --> 00:20:26.040
And lastly, it can become harder to refactor the code

00:20:26.040 --> 00:20:30.239
and to maintain as we'll have multiple languages being used.

00:20:31.719 --> 00:20:34.319
And to solve some of these challenges,

00:20:34.319 --> 00:20:36.680
what has been personally using

00:20:36.680 --> 00:20:41.680
is exploring different notebook editors

00:20:41.680 --> 00:20:46.680
and ideas that can make that type of workflow easier.

